    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Kristóf Batthyány (Vienna, 21 August
                    [1552])</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>He understands what Kristóf Batthyány wrote, and he has sent the prepared
                            letter to the King. He has spoken about the other cases with Ferenc
                            Batthyány, who said he would make sure the estates are prised from
                            Pálffy’s hands. Until then Ferenc Batthyány will cover the income those
                            estates would yield that year.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Magnifice Domine et Amice nobis Honorande, salutem!</p>
                <p>Ea, de quibus Dominatio Vestra nobis scripsit, intelleximus, litteras regiae
                    maiestatis pro Dominatione Vestra necessarias expeditas ad eam misimus. De aliis
                    rebus locuti fuimus nuper cum domino <persName>Francisco
                        Bathyany</persName>,<note type="critic">Ferenc Batthyány.</note> qui
                    respondit se curaturum esse, ut bona de manu <persName>Laurentii litterati
                        Palffy</persName><note type="critic">Lőrinc Pálffy († after 1557), often
                        called <hi rend="italic">litteratus</hi>, a prosecutor and a magistrate of
                        the Royal Court, see <hi rend="smallcap">Nagy</hi> 1862, 39.</note>
                    liberentur. Quae etiam in praesentia liberari non possunt, se tamen daturum esse
                    Dominationi Vestrae tantum, quantum proventus bonorum illorum hoc anno facerent.
                    Dominationem Vestra bene valere optamus.</p>
                <p>Datum <placeName>Viennae</placeName> 21. Augusti.</p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Vester Agriensis etc. propria manu</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p> Magnifico domino Christophoro de Bathyan, magistro pincernarum regiae maiestatis
                    etc. domino et amico nobis honorandissimo.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
